<statement><div><p>Consider the event of getting a number 7 when rolling a fair six-sided die. How would you classify this event?</p>

<p>[ Certain | Possible | Impossible ]  </p></div></statement>
<solution><div><h3>Worked Solution</h3>

<p>An event that must happen is called <alert>certain</alert>.</p>
<p>An event that cannot happen is called <alert>impossible</alert>.</p>
<p>An event that may or may not happen is called <alert>possible</alert>.</p>

<p>The correct classification of this event is <alert>Impossible</alert>.</p></div></solution>
<answer><p>Impossible</p></answer>
